            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# SuperScreenshot 0.9.82

- 将截图区域边框的拖动判定范围扩大到约 20px。
- 四角提供更宽的拖动判定范围。
- 新增横向、纵向和斜向缩放光标反馈。

---

- Expanded capture-bound resize hit areas to about 20px.
- Added larger corner drag targets.
- Added horizontal, vertical, and diagonal resize cursor feedback.
